ocale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the principal Act</citation> is amended by omitting the words <amend.in>control and supervision</amend.in>, and substituting the words <amend.in>control or supervision</amend.in>.</text>
          </para>
        </subprov>
      </prov.body>
    </prov>
